# AI Teaching App – Vision

## Problem
Students struggle to get immediate, personalized feedback while learning technical concepts.

## Solution
An AI-powered teaching assistant that explains concepts, quizzes users, adapts difficulty, and tracks learning progress.

## Target Users
- College CS students
- Self-taught programmers
- High school STEM students

## Core Value
Teach concepts clearly, adapt to the learner, and encourage understanding—not memorization.
